w.de on "My Arcade Blog for Mochiads"";s:4:"link";s:60:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/myarcadeblog/#post-11248";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Sat, 13 Jun 2009 21:30:32 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:12:"NetReview.de";}s:4:"guid";s:42:"11248@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:201:"MyArcadeBlog transforms your WordPress Blog into an arcade games site like <a href="http://fungames24.net" rel="nofollow">http://fungames24.net</a> using games from Mochiads. It published automatically";s:7:"summary";s:201:"MyArcadeBlog transforms your WordPress Blog into an arcade games site like <a href="http://fungames24.net" rel="nofollow">http://fungames24.net</a> using games from Mochiads. It published automatically";}i:8;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:25:"Zfen on "Quicktagzmilies"";s:4:"link";s:63:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/quicktagzmilies/#post-11320";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Wed, 17 Jun 2009 22:22:03 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:4:"Zfen";}s:4:"guid";s:42:"11320@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:50:"Adds a quicktag- and smileybar to your commentarea";s:7:"summary";s:50:"Adds a quicktag- and smileybar to your commentarea";}i:9;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:32:"pfefferle on "Save Microformats"";s:4:"link";s:63:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/save-microformats/#post-573";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Wed, 21 Mar 2007 01:35:16 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:9:"pfefferle";}s:4:"guid";s:40:"573@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:60:"A plugin to save posted Microformats using technorati feeds.";s:7:"summary";s:60:"A plugin to save posted Microformats using technorati feeds.";}i:10;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:19:"pfefferle on "APML"";s:4:"link";s:51:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/apml/#post-2623";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Wed, 28 Nov 2007 19:30:03 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:9:"pfefferle";}s:4:"guid";s:41:"2623@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:101:"This plugin creates an APML Feed using the the native WordPress-Tags, -Categories, -Links and -Feeds.";s:7:"summary";s:101:"This plugin creates an APML Feed using the the native WordPress-Tags, -Categories, -Links and -Feeds.";}i:11;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:32:"pfefferle on "Portable Contacts"";s:4:"link";s:64:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/portable-contacts/#post-7281";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Wed, 08 Oct 2008 13:17:13 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:9:"pfefferle";}s:4:"guid";s:41:"7281@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:104:"Some kind of Portable Contacts Delegation based on the awesome OpenID/Portable Contacts Demo by JanRain.";s:7:"summary";s:104:"Some kind of Portable Contacts Delegation based on the awesome OpenID/Portable Contacts Demo by JanRain.";}i:12;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:35:"pfefferle on "Ubiquity-Blog-Search"";s:4:"link";s:62:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/ubiquity-search/#post-6911";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Sat, 06 Sep 2008 15:56:50 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:9:"pfefferle";}s:4:"guid";s:41:"6911@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:82:"A plugin to let visitors search through your blog with the Ubiquity-Firefox-Addon.";s:7:"summary";s:82:"A plugin to let visitors search through your blog with the Ubiquity-Firefox-Addon.";}i:13;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:26:"shamekh on "Link Replacer"";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/link-replacer/#post-11325";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Thu, 18 Jun 2009 09:01:10 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:7:"shamekh";}s:4:"guid";s:42:"11325@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:71:"Add the links automatically in your post without using WYSIWYG editor .";s:7:"summary";s:71:"Add the links automatically in your post without using WYSIWYG editor .";}i:14;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:32:"Ivan Ovsyannikov on "Aphorismus"";s:4:"link";s:58:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/aphorismus/#post-11330";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Thu, 18 Jun 2009 11:29:36 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:16:"Ivan Ovsyannikov";}s:4:"guid";s:42:"11330@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:113:"The plug-in allows to deduce the random text block (aphorism) on pages, posts or sidebar. Plugin have the widget.";s:7:"summary";s:113:"The plug-in allows to deduce the random text block (aphorism) on pages, posts or sidebar. Plugin have the widget.";}}s:7:"channel";a:6:{s:5:"title";s:16:"Recently Updated";s:4:"link";s:36:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:16:"Recently Updated";s:8:"language";s:2:"en";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Sat, 20 Jun 2009 13:08:16 +0000";s:7:"tagline";s:16:"Recently Updated";}s:9:"textinput";a:0:{}s:5:"image";a:0:{}s:9:"feed_type";s:3:"RSS";s:12:"feed_version";s:3:"2.0";s:5:"stack";a:0:{}s:9:"inchannel";b:0;s:6:"initem";b:0;s:9:"incontent";b:0;s:11:"intextinput";b:0;s:7:"inimage";b:0;s:13:"current_field";s:0:"";s:17:"current_namespace";b:0;s:19:"_CONTENT_CONSTRUCTS";a:6:{i:0;s:7:"content";i:1;s:7:"summary";i:2;s:4:"info";i:3;s:5:"title";i:4;s:7:"tagline";i:5;s:9:"copyright";}}', 'no'),
