nd respect him. We should always think reverently of a Sadhu because a saintly person bestows peace of mind on us.', 'ABOUT', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-8', '', '', '2009-06-03 10:59:48', '2009-06-03 10:59:48', '', 2, 'http://www.gagangiriv1.com/2-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
