(48, 1, '2009-06-04 03:23:44', '2009-06-04 03:23:44', 'Shri Gagangiri''s teachings are simple yet profound based on his long years of rigorous penance &amp; direct knowledge.\r\n\r\nHe is the living embodiment of his messages. He continues to inspire many who go to him, by his own selfless divine life. He speaks in a very direct and simple language.\r\n\r\nThe words that flow from him are not based on scriptures or other sources but through direct experience having profound depth and meaning.\r\n\r\nHis teachings and philosophy have flowered through his close interaction with nature and people.\r\n\r\nFrom the serious seekers of self knowledge and God realisation, to the layman in search of peace and happiness in his daily life, all find something valuable to take and transform their lives.', 'TEACHINGS', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '24-revision-7', '', '', '2009-06-04 03:23:44', '2009-06-04 03:23:44', '', 24, 'http://www.gagangiriv1.com/24-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(49, 1, '2009-06-04 03:26:47', '2009-06-04 03:26:47', '<table border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="3" width="95%" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="header" colspan="2" align="left" valign="middle">Books</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="middle">Shri Gagangad Uvach (Experiences of the devotees)</td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="middle">Marathi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="middle">Chatanya Lahri (Aartis and Shlokas of Gagangiri Maharaj)</td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="middle">Marathi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody></table>', 'GALLERY', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-7', '', '', '2009-06-04 03:26:47', '2009-06-04 03:26:47', '', 11, 'http://www.gagangiriv1.com/11-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(50, 1, '2009-06-04 03:38:36', '2009-06-04 03:38:36', 'It is also a regular rest and refreshment stop for motorists traveling on the Mumbai-Pune Highway (officially National Highway 4).\r\n\r\nKhopoli railway station is a railhead, meaning that the suburban railway line from Mumbai ends here. For long distance trains, shuttles, and regular suburban trains, the nearest junction is Karjat. The town is also well-connected by road since it lies on National Highway 4.\r\n\r\nA direct bus to Khopoli leaves early in the morning from Mumbai Central. Alternatively Volvo Bus service to Pune stop in Khopoli, from where one can take an Auto to the Ashram\r\nBy Air : 	Nearest airport is Pune.\r\nBy Rail : 	Nearest railhead is Khopoli\r\nBy Road : 	Mumbai-Khopoli	89 kms.\r\nPune-Khopoli		74 kms.\r\nLonavala-Khopoli	12 kms.\r\nKarjat - Khopli 	10 kms', 'PLAN A TRIP', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '35-revision-4', '', '', '2009-06-04 03:38:36', '2009-06-04 03:38:36', '', 35, 'http://www.gagangiriv1.com/35-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
