(83, 1, '2009-06-04 09:29:49', '2009-06-04 09:29:49', 'Maharaja takes keen interest in the History of these periods. His knowledge &amp; insight of the working of these periods is awesome. When he speaks about them, it is as if he was in that era.\r\n\r\nShri Gagangiri''s Links with history\r\nSpan three periods from the era :\r\n<p><ul>\r\n	<li>Samrat Chalukya Pulkeshi in the 1100''s</li>\r\n	<li>Sardar Nagojirao Patankar</li>\r\n	<li>Pant Amatya Bavdekar, Samarth Ramdas &amp; Shivaji Maharaj.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>', 'GURUJI''S LINK WITH HISTORY ', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gurujis-link-with-history', '', '', '2009-06-04 09:31:42', '2009-06-04 09:31:42', '', 2, 'http://www.gagangiriv1.com/?page_id=83', 3, 'page', '', 0),
