(103, 1, '2009-06-04 09:48:48', '2009-06-04 09:48:48', 'Most of the Ashrams are taken care by P.P. Swami Kille Gagangad Charitible trust or P.P. Swami religious trust\r\nOr either in their own small and simple individual capacity. ', ' ADMINISTRATION ', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'administration', '', '', '2009-06-04 09:48:48', '2009-06-04 09:48:48', '', 2, 'http://www.gagangiriv1.com/?page_id=103', 7, 'page', '', 0),
