(210, 1, '2009-06-04 09:58:39', '2009-06-04 09:58:39', 'Shri Gagangiri''s teachings are simple yet profound based on his long years of rigorous penance &amp; direct knowledge.\r\n\r\nHe is the living embodiment of his messages. He continues to inspire many who go to him, by his own selfless divine life. He speaks in a very direct and simple language.\r\n\r\nThe words that flow from him are not based on scriptures or other sources but through direct experience having profound depth and meaning.\r\n\r\nHis teachings and philosophy have flowered through his close interaction with nature and people.\r\n\r\nFrom the serious seekers of self knowledge and God realisation, to the layman in search of peace and happiness in his daily life, all find something valuable to take and transform their lives.', 'TEACHINGS', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '24-revision-12', '', '', '2009-06-04 09:58:39', '2009-06-04 09:58:39', '', 24, 'http://www.gagangiriv1.com/24-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
